    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> [2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and <strong>pepper strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until softened</p>",
