            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper and onion have softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong> and your <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1998.-step-4-x200.jpg",
