            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce thickens, chop your <strong>wholemeal pitta[s]</strong> into triangles</p><p>Add the <strong>pitta triangles</strong> to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 8-10 min or until the pitta is crunchy and toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1998.-step-6.2-x200.jpg",
