            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spinach<strong> </strong>has wilted, make 1 well per person in the tomato sauce and crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into it, then cook, covered for 2-3 min or until the egg is done to your liking – this is your <strong>spiced shakshuka</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
