        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spiced</strong> <strong>shakshuka </strong>with the<strong> toasted pitta</strong> <strong>triangles</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with your<strong> pumpkin seeds</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Crumble over your <strong>feta</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
